\c 124 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 124\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Gargaarsa Waaqayyoo Yaadatanii Galateeffachuu (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an; kan Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* "Inni gara keenya gore Waaqayyo utuu ta'uu dhabaatee" haa jedhu sabni Israa'el.
\m \bd 2\bd* Yeroo namoonni nu irratti ka'an, "Inni gara keenya gore Waaqayyo utuu ta'uu dhabaatee
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*\bd 3\bd* silaa yeroo aariin isaanii nu irratti boba'e sana, isaan fayyaatti nu in liqimsu turan.
\m \bd 4\bd* Silaa lolaan nu fudhatee in sokka, bishaan bubbisus mataa keenya irra in yaa'a ture.
\m \bd 5\bd* Silaa huursaan bishaanii, mataa keenya irra in yaa'a ture.
\m \bd 6\bd* Waaqayyo inni afaan isaanii keessa nu hin buusin, ulfinaan haa jajamu!
\m \bd 7\bd* Akka simbirroonni kiyyoo adamsituu jalaa baatu, nuyis isaan jalaa in baane kiyyichi in ciccite, nuyis jalaa in baane.
\m \bd 8\bd* Maqaa Waaqayyoo isa waaqaa fi lafa uumeen, nuyi gargaarsa arganne.
\b 
